<eesti>Olemasolev k&auml;itis </eesti>
<inglise>Existing installations </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Olemasolev k&auml;itis on k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumise ajal tegutsev k&auml;itis ning k&auml;itis, mille k&auml;itajal on enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist saadud &otilde;igusaktide kohased tegevus- ja keskkonnaload ning kus alustatakse tegevust hiljemalt aasta jooksul p&auml;rast k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) "Existing installation" means an installation in operation or an installation whose operator holds all relevant activity and environmental licences in compliance with the legislation existing before this Act enters into force, provided that such installation is put into operation not later than one year after the date on which this Act enters into force. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Olemasoleva k&auml;itise k&auml;itaja peab esitama kompleksloa taotluse loa andjale hiljemalt Vabariigi Valitsuse m&auml;&auml;rusega kehtestatud t&auml;htajaks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The operator of an existing installation shall submit an application to the issuer of permits not later than by the term established by a regulation of the Government of the Republic. </inglise>
<eesti>Ajavahemik k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest kuni esitamise t&auml;htajani ei tohi olla l&uuml;hem kui &uuml;ks aasta. </eesti>
<inglise>The period of time between the entry into force of this Act and the term for submission of the applications shall not be less than one year. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Selgituse saamiseks kompleksloa taotluse esitamise vajalikkuse v&otilde;i esitamise t&auml;htp&auml;eva kohta p&ouml;&ouml;rdub k&auml;itaja loa andja poole. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) An operator shall make inquiries to the issuer of permits to clarify whether or not the operator needs to submit an application, or in order to find out the term for submission of an application. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 2 nimetatud kohustuse t&auml;itmata j&auml;tmise korral peatatakse k&auml;itise tegevus keskkonnaj&auml;relevalve seaduses (RT I 2001, 56, 337) s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Upon failure to perform the duty specified in subsection (2) of this section, the operation of an installation shall be suspended pursuant to the procedure provided for in the Environmental Supervision Act (RT I 2001, 56, 337). </inglise>
<eesti>(5) Kui loa andja tuvastab, et k&auml;itises ei kasutata kompleksloa taotluse esitamise ajal parimat v&otilde;imalikku tehnikat, tehakse k&auml;itajale lisaks k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 17 s&auml;testatule kohustuseks koostada tehniliste &uuml;mberkorralduste kava parima v&otilde;imaliku tehnika rakendamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) If the issuer of permits establishes that the best available techniques are not used in an installation at the time of submission of an application, the operator shall be required, in addition to the performance of the duties provided for in &sect; 17 of this Act, to prepare a plan for technological restructuring for the implementation of the best available techniques. </inglise>
<eesti>Kava peab sisaldama meetmeid ka k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 9 l&otilde;ikes 3 nimetatud &otilde;igusaktide n&otilde;uete t&auml;itmiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>The plan shall also contain measures for compliance with the legislation specified in subsection 9 (3) of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Loa andja kas kiidab kava heaks ja m&auml;&auml;rab selle alusel heite piirv&auml;&auml;rtused ja meetmete rakendamise t&auml;htajad igaks kalendriaastaks v&otilde;i tagastab kava &uuml;mbertegemiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>The issuer of permits shall either approve the plan and determine emission limit values on the basis thereof and terms for the application of measures for each calendar year, or shall return the plan for the making of corrections. </inglise>
<eesti>Tegevuskava abin&otilde;ude rakendamise tulemusel peab k&auml;itis toimima parima v&otilde;imaliku tehnika n&otilde;uete kohaselt hiljemalt 2007. aasta 30. oktoobriks. </eesti>
<inglise>As a result of application of the measures provided for in the action plan, an installation shall operate in compliance with the requirements of the best available techniques at the latest by 30 October 2007. </inglise>
<eesti>(6) K&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 5 nimetatud tehniliste &uuml;mberkorralduste kava esitab taotleja loa andjale koos kompleksloa taotlusega. </eesti>
<inglise>(6) An operator shall submit the plan for technological restructuring specified in subsection (5) of this section to the issuer of permits together with an application for a permit. </inglise>
<eesti>(7) Kui tehnilisi &uuml;mberkorraldusi ei ole k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 5 nimetatud t&auml;htajaks v&otilde;imalik majanduslikel v&otilde;i tehnilistel p&otilde;hjustel teha, peab k&auml;itaja esitama kompleksloa taotluse keskkonnaministrile, kes otsustab kompleksloa andmise k&auml;esolevas seaduses s&auml;testatud korras. </eesti>
<inglise>(7) If technological restructuring cannot be completed by the term specified in subsection (5) of this section due to economical or technical reasons, the operator shall submit an application for a permit to the Minister of the Environment who shall decide on the grant thereof pursuant to the procedure provided for in this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>Kompleksluba peab sel juhul sisaldama tehniliste &uuml;mberkorralduste kava. </eesti>
<inglise>In such case, a permit shall contain a plan for technological restructuring. </inglise>
<eesti>K&auml;itaja tegevust tehniliste &uuml;mberkorralduste kava elluviimisel j&auml;lgib loa andja. </eesti>
<inglise>The issuer of permits shall monitor the activities of an operator in the implementation of the plan for technological restructuring. </inglise>
